com.sri.ai.expresso.api

Interface IntensionalSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<Object>, Expression, QuantifiedExpression, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractIntensionalSet, DefaultIntensionalMultiSet, DefaultIntensionalUniSet

    @Beta
public interface IntensionalSet
extends QuantifiedExpression
    An Expression that represents an intensionally defined set.

    An object E belongs to an intensionally defined set { (on I) H | C } if and only if there is a value I' for the index expressions I such that I' satisfies C and E = H(I'), where H(I') is the result of replacing I by I' in H.

    Author:
    braz
